- Color thresholds in draftUtils.ts:
  fortyColor: gold ≤4.38s / green ≤4.50s / orange ≤4.65s
  benchColor: gold ≥28 reps / green ≥22 / orange ≥15
  vertColor:  gold ≥40" / green ≥36" / orange ≥32"
  coneColor:  gold ≤6.80s / green ≤7.10s / orange ≤7.40s
