PLAYER LIFECYCLE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
- Contracts: salary (AAV), years remaining, guaranteed/dead cap
- Morale: 0–100, updated seasonally, affects sim via OVR multiplier
- Franchise Tag / Transition Tag: premium 1-year lock (see Offseason Tab)
- Injuries: random in-game; auto-callup from PS covers starters
- Waiver Wire: CPU claims by worst-record priority
- Progression / Regression: dev trait ceiling, age-based regression,
  breakout bonuses for standout seasons
- Practice Squad Development: age ≤23 PS players get up to +3 OVR bonus
- Season Awards: 6 awards computed at season advance; MVP + DPOY fire news
- Retirement + HOF: age/OVR thresholds; career milestone induction check

